{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"724c4bdca8","title":"在苏联莫斯科大剧院的庆祝大会上的祝词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4248ae37c3","index":0,"year":1949,"month":12,"day":21,"articleId":"724c4bdca8","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1949-1957卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"edb872e029","type":"title","text":"在苏联莫斯科大剧院的庆祝大会上的祝词","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"42f7141642","type":"paragraph","text":"亲爱的同志们，朋友们：","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae778b67c6","type":"paragraph","text":"我这次有可能参加庆祝斯大林同志七十寿辰的盛会，衷心至为愉快。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b24818c9b8","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林同志是世界人民的导师和朋友，也是中国．收的导师和朋友。他发展了马克思一一列宁主义理论，并对于世界共产主义运动的事业作了极其杰出和极其宽广的贡献。中国人民在反抗压迫者的艰苦斗争中深切地感到斯大林同志的友谊的重要性。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"11d5287d4b","type":"paragraph","text":"在这个盛会上，我谨以中国人民和中国共产党的名义庆祝斯大林同志的七十寿辰，祝福他的健康和长寿，祝福我们伟大友邻苏联在斯大林同志领导下的幸福和强盛。并欢呼世界工人阶级在斯大林同志领导下的空前大团结。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b169d36165","type":"paragraph","text":"世界工人阶级和国际主义运动的领袖－－伟大的斯大林万岁!","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dcd67a5635","type":"paragraph","text":"世界和平与民主的堡垒苏联万岁!","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"724c4bdca8","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":15,"end":14}}}},"__N_SSG":true}